    "was consulted to decide if the article should be selected.",
    "A total of 53 articles were reduced, resulting in 728 articles that underwent the second round of screening.",
    "In the second round of screening, a thorough evaluation of the 728 articles' eligibility was carried out through full-text reading based on the same screening process by the three authors (X.C., X.T., and H.X.)",
